Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 06 of Hip MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Synovia, mass' from the dropdown menu
Then 'I describe' radio button is enabled and preselected
And 'I know' radio button is enabled
And 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Characterization I' tab is enabled and preselected
And 'Characterization II' tab is enabled
And 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And 'Diffuse' radio button is enabled
And 'Focal' radio button is enabled

And 'Size' input field is enabled
And '2nd plane' input field is enabled
And '3rd plane' input field is enabled
And 'Sharp' radio button is enabled
And 'Ill defined' radio button is enabled
And 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled

And 'Round' radio button is enabled
And 'Lobulated' radio button is enabled
And 'Multilobulated' radio button is enabled

And 'T1w signal' slide bar is enabled
And 'T2w signal' slide bar is enabled

And 'Necrosis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Susceptibility artifacts' checkbox is enabled
And 'Synovial nodulus' checkbox is enabled
And 'Synovial proliferations' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Susceptibility artifacts' checkbox
Then 'Blooming artifact' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Synovial nodulus' checkbox
Then '> 1 lesion, same pathology' checkbox is enabled
